# Lint/type-check tooling for the CI "lint" job.
# Runtime deps (pydantic, defusedxml, xmlschema) are included so mypy
# --strict can resolve the models' types rather than treating them as
# untyped. ruff/black are pinned to the exact versions the CI lint job
# uses so the check stays deterministic across uv recompiles.
